title: Sheep and Other Anomalies - Discography
description:
This is a collection of music by me (Sheep). It&#039;s not very good but that&#039;s kinda my thing. I play mostly acoustic, with a few techno type songs on my second album. This collection contains my first 2 CDs, a comp that I&#039;m on, and an extra song I recorded for the same people who put me on the comp. It&#039;s a mixture of nerdy and comedy music, my influences come from folk, punk, ska, and other assorted genres. I don&#039;t ask for any money, not even donations, this is completely free music. You might like it, you might not but it&#039;s free so why not give it a listen? If you&#039;re interested check out my myspace page: http://myspace.com/anarchyshoe

Thanks and Enjoy!
-Sheep
